Hey everyone! Cerbotics 4400, Space Cookies 1868 and Under Control 1156 are organizing an FRC Warm-Up event. Warm-Up is a series of free conferences, in which well-known people and teams from FIRST address topics of vital importance for the performance and development of any other team. The event is from January 2nd - 4th, from 10:00 AM to 1:00PM CST time zone. Make sure to register and stay tuned to their social media to learn more about the teams who are participating!

¡Hola equipos! 

Aquí podrás realizar tu registro para el evento. No olvides llenar todo con cuidado y con los datos correctos. Recuerda invitar a todos tus compañeros y mentores!
 
---------------------------

Hi teams!

Here you will find the sign...
